snippet.title: Digital Portrait Painting In IbisPaint X - Amber Heard | Grid Method IbisPaint X | Ibis Painter Sara
snippet.description:
Digital Portrait of 'Amber Heard' on IbisPaint-X in iPad! In this Portrait you can see An Easy way to Draw the Sketch in 'Grid Method' & with each Minute Details, a Perfect Color gradation & Realistic Shading. 

To Complete the Portrait it took me 5 Days!
